Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:57.46,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}獨自在意著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}せつないだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.38,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}也只會徒增傷悲
